to install:

0. install IBus: 
http://ibus.googlecode.com/

1. in your shell: 
cd ibus-zime
sudo make install

2. install the schema of your choice:
cd data
./create-schema.py pinyin-schema.txt pinyin-keywords.txt pinyin-phrases.txt
./create-schema.py zhuyin-schema.txt zhuyin-keywords.txt zhuyin-phrases.txt
./create-schema.py -k combo-pinyin-schema.txt
./make-phrases.py jyutping
./create-schema.py jyutping-schema.txt jyutping-keywords.txt jyutping-phrases.txt
# your resulting SQLite database is located in ~/.ibus/zime/zime.db

3. restart IBus and enable ZIME engine in IBus preferences.

4. when ZIME is running, type Ctrl+` to call schema chooser.

documentation is coming, later.
questions go to chen.sst@gmail.com
